All Implemented Interfaces:
IEnhancedSearchTopicItemResult, com.mobius.vdrapi.IHasConnectionState, INode, IPageFactory
public class EnhancedSearchTopicItemNode
extends PageFactoryNode
implements IEnhancedSearchTopicItemResult

A EnhancedSearchTopicItemNode object represents a single page of a document, referenced by parsing all the different parameters returned from a SearchTopicItemListFactory createList call with a EnhancedSearchTopicItemQueryParam QueryParam. Where the search result is more than one page, the Search TopicItemNode object represents the first page of the result, and indicates the number of pages that follow.

This class is similar to SearchTopicItemNode
